data.title: Alamo Guide: Sept-Oct 2008
data.meta_description: Alamo Guide: Sept-Oct 2008 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document appears to be an entertainment guide listing upcoming films, showtimes, and events in Austin, Texas between September 12th and November 1st, 2008. Highlights include the openings of films like Burn After Reading, City of Ember, and Igor, as well as ongoing events like the Fantastic Fest film festival and the Rocky Horror Picture Show. Various theaters are featured hosting movies, quote-alongs, and other programs.
